{"tid":748590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專營權屆滿明結業 600澳門狗被送返大陸","createTime":"2018-07-19T10:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T11:20:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51e21e16d47ed80ea8e40a856fa2e63d85149c39","tid":748590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"澳門逸園賽狗專營權將於明日（20日）屆滿，逸園賽狗場亦將於21日結業，外界一直關注的600多隻格力犬去向未明。本報今日多次嘗試狗會了解格力犬最新情況及去向，但暫未聯絡上。早前澳門傳媒報道，大批格力犬將會移送至海南省安置，又引述逸園執行董事梁安琪指，珠海會接收餘下的犬隻。<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府發言人辦公室昨日聯同博彩監察協調局、民政總署、土地工務運輸局、體育局及財政局舉行記者會，其中博彩監察協調局表示，狗會必須不遲於明日遷離狗場，如狗會決定續辦賽狗活動，需另覓新址，並要改善對格力犬飼養條件等，該局會與狗會保持溝通，並關注格力犬的去向等。<br />\n<br />\n民政總署亦在記者會上指，賽狗專營權雖然於明日終結，但並非代表逸園公司履行企業責任的終結，該公司仍是600多頭格力犬的主人，須無條件為未被領養的格力犬提供安置及照顧，及尋找理想領養出路，總署強調格力犬是逸園公司的「員工」，該公司不應推卸責任；又重申會按《動物保護法》做好監管工作，如出現棄養情況，署方亦會按法例提出檢控，確保退役格力犬在任何情況下都不會無家可歸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180719&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58462240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180719%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58462240&d=ZLe4iOmHm5XT7L3rTUyYzS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a3d83bfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180719%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58462240&h=cc53dac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180719&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58462240</a>"},{"pid":"8427acf98e44b8107983d915fe1add5f999770c9","tid":748590,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"大把狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a830be288e8c0e5fdabaaa0c0fd25defccac82b2","tid":748590,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8427acf98e44b8107983d915fe1add5f999770c9","tid":748590,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"大把狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"走地狗　　做慣運動"},{"pid":"4e86485fc35da499b6afc111a105461658a5f5ab","tid":748590,"uid":92603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"標題笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b773bedb3847c1f3090ebb357727e5f0fd9d4345","tid":748590,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8427acf98e44b8107983d915fe1add5f999770c9","tid":748590,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"大把狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"養到狗肉節開餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56b2e96a06e07bb9662deb8482c782f0d296c43","tid":748590,"uid":76681,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"語帶相關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34445bc5703f4c6bcd2de5ddb9e2f93a11f1982c","tid":748590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}